4 Hours Ago AI urged the Nigerian government to do more in protecting Nigerians and ensure perpetrators are brought to justice. "Boko Haram and other armed groups must renounce their unlawful and vicious campaign of violence against civilians. The Nigerian authorities, on their part, must do more to protect civilians and bring the perpetrators of all such attacks to justice," AI said. 